-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SecLists                                              {rockyou is in /Passwords/Leaked-Databases   && Extract w/ {tar xvzf rockyou.txt.tar.gz}
          https://github.com/danielmiessler/SecLists
Kali 
          /usr/share/wordlists
